title: 2018 European Junior Judo Championships
text:
The 2018 <a href="European%20Junior%20Judo%20Championships">European Junior Judo Championships</a> is an edition of the <a href="European%20Junior%20Judo%20Championships">European Junior Judo Championships</a>, organised by the <a href="European%20Judo%20Union">European Judo Union</a>.It was held in <a href="Sofia">Sofia</a>, <a href="Bulgaria">Bulgaria</a> from 13 to 16 September 2018.
